Edmond Beauchamp https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edmond_Beauchamp 0 Edmond Beauchamp (3 March 1900 – 3 June 1985), sometimes credited only as Beauchamp, was a French film and Broadway stage actor. He appeared in 70 films between 1928 and 1979. Edmond_Beauchamp ( 3_March_1900 – 3_June_1985 ) , sometimes_credited only as Beauchamp , was a_French_film and Broadway_stage_actor .
